data.name: lbltxtAbout.Text
data.value:
FEP Job Runner is a tool for testing various APIs and Integrations of Fidelis Endpoint. It's homepage is located at: https://github.com/bmartin5692/FEP-Job-Runner
This program utilizes the following third-party libraries: -Newtonsoft Json.Net for all JSON creation. More info can be found at http://www.newtonsoft.com/json
-RestSharp for all RestAPI calls. More info can be found at http://restsharp.org
-FEPRestClient for interacting with the Fidelis Endpoint Rest API. More info can be found at https://github.com/bmartin5692/FEP-RestAPI-Net
